trans-unit.source: Represents an Application Menu that is used in a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en program-menyen som brukes i en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Every ribbon includes an Application Menu as the first tab in the ribbon.
trans-unit.target: Hver båndet inneholder et webprogram-menyen som den første kategorien på båndet.

trans-unit.source: Other ribbon tabs contain controls for working with the document content.
trans-unit.target: Andre båndet kategoriene inneholder kontroller for å arbeide med innholdet i dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: In contrast, the Application Menu presents a menu of commands for working with the file.
trans-unit.target: I motsetning viser webprogram-menyen en meny med kommandoer for å arbeide med filen.

trans-unit.source: Examples include commands that traditionally go in the File menu to create, open, save, and print files.
trans-unit.target: Eksempler på kommandoer som vanligvis går inn i filen menyen for å opprette, åpne, lagre og skrive ut filer.

trans-unit.source: It is also used to access program options and the Exit command.
trans-unit.target: Den brukes også til å få tilgang til alternativer og Avslutt-kommando.

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows the Application Menu for a ribbon control.
trans-unit.target: Illustrasjonen nedenfor viser webprogram-menyen for en kontroll på båndet.

trans-unit.source: ![Ribbon Application Menu](~/add/media/wpfribbon-appmenu.png "Ribbon Application Menu") The RibbonApplicationMenu can host <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenuItem> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationSplitMenuItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: ![Applikasjons-menyen på båndet](~/add/media/wpfribbon-appmenu.png "båndet webprogram menyen") for RibbonApplicationMenu kan være vert for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenuItem>og <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationSplitMenuItem>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationSplitMenuItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenuItem>

trans-unit.source: The Application Menu also has an *auxiliary pane* and a *footer pane* that can host additional content.
trans-unit.target: Applikasjons-menyen har også en *Aux ruten* og en *bunntekst ruten* som kan tilby mer innhold.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenu.AuxiliaryPaneContent%2A> property hosts a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonGallery> and is typically used to display a list of recent documents.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenu.AuxiliaryPaneContent%2A>egenskapen verter en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonGallery>og brukes vanligvis til å vise en liste over nylige dokumenter.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonGallery> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenu.AuxiliaryPaneContent%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenu.FooterPaneContent%2A> property typically hosts buttons that enable access to program options and the Exit command.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenu.FooterPaneContent%2A>egenskapen vert vanligvis knapper som gjør tilgang til alternativer og Avslutt-kommando.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonApplicationMenu.FooterPaneContent%2A>
